The purpose of this project is to allow users the ability to create a Christmas Shopping List.
Items can be removed or added to the Christmas Shopping List at any time.
If the user is interested in removing an item from the list, the user can select the "Remove" button, next to the item, to remove the item.
If the user is interested in adding an Item the user can select the "Add Item" button to add an item.
When the user selects the "Add Item" button. A modal will appear asking the user to enter the item name.
After the user enters the item name the user can click on the "Add to List" button to add the item to the Christmas Shopping List.
If the user selects the "Add Item" button and chooses not to add an item to the list. The user can select the (x) button to exit.
Have fun creating your Christmas Shopping List!

